561
00:48:16,389 --> 00:48:17,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Soo Man,</font>

562
00:48:18,389 --> 00:48:19,999
<font color=#FFFF00>kamu pasti senang melihat menantumu.</font>

563
00:48:21,229 --> 00:48:23,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Tahun depan, kita akan melakukan peringatan kematianmu</font>

