00:55:09,369 --> 00:55:10,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Seo Won!</font>

621
00:55:11,809 --> 00:55:12,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Seo Won!</font>

622
00:55:13,780 --> 00:55:15,410
<font color=#FFFF00>Seo Won!</font>

623
00:55:15,610 --> 00:55:17,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Seo Won, berhenti.</font>

624
00:55:17,650 --> 00:55:19,650
<font color=#FFFF00>- Tolong berhenti. Maafkan aku./- Lepaskan aku!</font>

625
00:55:20,079 --> 00:55:21,349
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada apa denganmu?</font>

626
00:55:24,320 --> 00:55:26,059
<font color=#FFFF00>- Lepaskan aku!/- Maafkan aku.</font>

