<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

628
00:55:31,329 --> 00:55:32,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Semua salahku.</font>

629
00:55:35,260 --> 00:55:36,269
<font color=#FFFF00>- Lepaskan!/- Seo Won.</font>

630
00:55:42,300 --> 00:55:43,539
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku.</font>

631
00:56:41,499 --> 00:56:43,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku biasanya tidak tertidur di mobil.</font>

632
00:56:44,999 --> 00:56:47,599
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu karena minuman murni dari Kakek.</font>

633
00:56:48,970 --> 00:56:50,470
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

634
00:56:50,470 --> 00:56:52,070
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu merasa segar sekarang?</font>

635
00:56:55,380 --> 00:56:57,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Rasanya seperti tidur di kamarku.</font>

636
00:56:57,880 --> 00:56:58,910
<font color=#FFFF00>Baguslah.</font>

637
00:57:00,320 --> 00:57:01,380
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya.</font>

638
00:57:12,800 --> 00:57:14,059
<font color=#FFFF00>Pil Joo.</font>

639
00:57:17,300 --> 00:57:18,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih.</font>

640
00:57:23,639 --> 00:57:25,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena telah baik kepada Boo Cheon.</font>

641
00:57:28,340 --> 00:57:31,610
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa aku tahu sedikit</font>

642
00:57:32,720 --> 00:57:34,419
<font color=#FFFF00>kenapa Boo Cheon mengandalkanmu.</font>

643
00:57:36,349 --> 00:57:37,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebenarnya,</font>

644
00:57:38,749 --> 00:57:41,119
<font color=#FFFF00>aku tidak memercayaimu</font>

645
00:57:42,019 --> 00:57:44,090
<font color=#FFFF00>sejak tahu kamu dan Boo Cheon bertukar nama.</font>

646
00:57:49,630 --> 00:57:50,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Maaf.</font>

647
00:57:54,769 --> 00:57:56,169
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang harus meminta maaf.</font>

648
00:58:04,110 --> 00:58:05,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah.</font>

649
00:58:46,059 --> 00:58:49,459
<font color=#FFFF00>"Mooshimwon"</font>

650
00:59:03,269 --> 00:59:05,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Pergilah ke Kuil Cheongnyang.</font>

651
00:59:06,439 --> 00:59:08,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu kuil kecil di Gunung Bukhan.</font>

652
00:59:08,880 --> 00:59:09,880
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita ke sana.</font>

653
00:59:13,519 --> 00:59:14,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin</font>

654
00:59:15,419 --> 00:59:17,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah akan memasang papan nama di kuil besar</font>

655
00:59:18,249 --> 00:59:21,660
<font color=#FFFF00>dan membuat kehebohan dengan bertindak mencolok.</font>

656
00:59:23,189 --> 00:59:26,260
<font color=#FFFF00>"Aku menghargai semangat putraku."</font>

657
00:59:26,999 --> 00:59:28,430
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia ingin masuk berita</font>

658
00:59:29,130 --> 00:59:31,470
<font color=#FFFF00>dengan kisah memilukan.</font>

659
00:59:33,400 --> 00:59:36,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Suamiku tidak suka keributan.</font>

660
00:59:38,610 --> 00:59:40,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia pria pendiam yang menyukai hutan.</font>

661
00:59:42,039 --> 00:59:43,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia juga menyukai kuil itu.</font>

662
00:59:46,619 --> 00:59:47,979
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo lihat seperti apa kuil itu.</font>

663
01:00:09,139 --> 01:00:10,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Senang bertemu denganmu.</font>

664
01:00:30,990 --> 01:00:33,900
<font color=#FFFF00>"Jang Kyung Cheon"</font>

665
01:00:36,669 --> 01:00:39,970
<font color=#FFFF00>"Adikku tersayang, Jang Kyung Cheon"</font>

666
01:00:50,809 --> 01:00:51,849
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin diam-diam kemari</font>

667
01:00:52,550 --> 01:00:54,780
<font color=#FFFF00>untuk menemuinya pada peringatan kematiannya.</font>

668
01:00:54,780 --> 01:00:56,749
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, silakan.</font>

669
01:00:57,090 --> 01:01:00,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Pengacara Kang akan mengatakan sisanya.</font>

670
01:01:02,660 --> 01:01:03,689
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi.</font>

671
01:01:40,930 --> 01:01:43,999
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus kembali ke kantor.</font>

672
01:01:44,769 --> 01:01:47,169
<font color=#FFFF00>Presdir Jang Seong Man ingin bertemu denganku.</font>

673
01:02:01,419 --> 01:02:03,249
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu ingat Jang Kyung Cheon?</font>

674
01:02:04,689 --> 01:02:06,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pergi ke kuil yang sering dikunjungi suamiku.</font>

675
01:02:08,260 --> 01:02:10,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Papan nama Jang Kyung Cheon ada di sana.</font>

676
01:02:13,559 --> 01:02:15,329
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu harus mencoba menemukan Jang Eun Cheon lagi.</font>

